metadata.name: YELLOW SPIRIT
metadata.description:
The Junglesoul concept started in the fishing village Itacaré, state of Bahia.Brasil
 I adapted this concept to photographic projects specially in Amazon that you will discover in the next collections 

The Smoke colors effect was produced by means of colored smoke . Post production a mirror effect to give a face to the spirit of the jungle. Shot in Itacaré , Bahia Brasil .Digital image shot with a Canon 5D MIII
